[DECLINED] Incorrect works indents for lists, example:
<li>
<p>Kristina</p>
</li>
*/

/*
[INFO] That the bullets not lost on mobile version
ol
ul
	list-style-position inside
*/
ol
ul
	/* [ACTION] Smaller indentation between list items:
	https://stackoverflow.com/a/28597518/5951529

	[PURPOSE] On mobile devices indentation takes up too much area
	*/
	padding-left .7rem
